                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18241202-135-defend870 t18241202-135-deflabel757"></join>; he was to receive the money from my customers, and to settle with me every evening. I had a customer named Baker - on the 23d of November the prisoner left my service; he had been with me about nine months.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18241202-135-person872">
                  MARY 
                  ANN HARDING
